  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large Dutch oven, melt the vegan butter over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms, chopped onion, and minced garlic, and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the vegetable broth, thyme, rosemary, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Cover the Dutch oven and transfer it to the preheated oven.",
    "Braise the stew for 30 minutes, or until the flavors have melded together and the mushrooms are tender.",
    "Remove the stew from the oven and let it cool slightly.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired, on a slate tile vessel."
